= TTF_OpenFontRW =

Open a font file from a SDL_RWops.

== Syntax ==

<syntaxhighlight lang='c'>
TTF_Font * TTF_OpenFontRW(SDL_RWops *src, int freesrc, int ptsize);
</syntaxhighlight>

== Function Parameters ==

{|
|'''src'''
|SDL_RWops to use. 'src' must be kept alive for the lifetime of the [[TTF_Font]].
|-
|'''freesrc'''
|can be set so that [[TTF_CloseFont]] closes the RWops
|-
|'''ptsize'''
|point size
|}

== Return Value ==

Returns a valid [[TTF_Font]], NULL on error

